game.name: Unblock That
game.description:
Join Unblock That right away and forget all the brain teasers you previously tried online in your gaming devices during your free hours! The new thing is the unique solution for each puzzle you find in this brand new arcade game. There are multiple levels combined with the brain-storming and challenging difficulties to deal with. Get ready to solve various difficult puzzles by testing your skills and abilities in a way like never before! All you need to do is just clear a path for the brown-colored block.

Drag and swipe the wooden blocks within the given space to create a path for your brown colored block in this HTML5 sliding-puzzle game! Be careful since you would have to achieve your target with the help of limited moves! You can complete each level with 3 stars rating only if you use the limited moves to complete your game. Use the hints if you find it unable to solve the puzzle in this addictive puzzle challenge!

The blocks which you can move have light wooden color while the blocks which you have to take out of the given board have dark wooden colors. The dark wooden block reaches the exit gate when there has a path. Try to put your best to collect all 3 stars in all the levels of this cute brain teaser challenge! No need to get bored since we cover almost all the classic and latest arcade games where your puzzle-solving abilities would be tested to the optimum level. Play alone or invite your friends to have a blast online without download!
